description: OamIpSupport: Table recording the IP address change status and supporting ID for OAM IP support in different cells at specific timestamps.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp of record), Area_Name (cell area name), CellId (unique cell identifier), Id2 (duplicate of CellId), Id3 (likely an internal identifier), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (data format version), OamIpSupport.ipAddressChangeStatus (status of IP address change), OamIpSupport.oamIpSupportId (OAM IP support identifier).
